For Window and Linux OS

Dependency libraries:
- Qt (> 4.8, included OpenGL) 
- OpenCV (> 2.4.2) 
[- OpenCL (>5.0 for NVIDIA) for GPGPU] 

Builds and run:
- modify path in file "Ipm.pro"
- qmake => create a makefile (must)
- make => build program

=============================================================
NOTE
=============================================================

Version 1.0
=============================================================
Algorithms:
	- To grayscale img
	- To binary img
	- Roberts
	- Sobel
	- Hit and miss
	- Otsu
	- Region growing
	- Social ant
Using opencv
	- smooth
		- normal Blur
		- gaussian Blur
		- median Blur
		- bilateral Filter
		- convolution Filter
	- morphology
		- erosion
		- dilation
		- opening
		- closing
		- morphological gradient
		- top Hat
		- black Hat
	- transformation
		- pyramid
		- remap
		- affine
	- segmentation
		- threshold
		- Sobel
		- Scharr
		- laplace
		- Canny
		- hough cine
		- hough circle
		- find contour
		- convex Hull
		- bounding box and circle
		- bounding rotate and eclipse
		- image moments
	- point, feature detector
		- Harris
		- Shi-Tomasi
		- Corner detect
		- SURF feature detector
		- SIFT feature detector
		- feature description
		- feature detect with FLANN
		- Homography to find feature
		- template matching
	- histogram
		- histogram calculate
		- equalization
		- back projection
